{"tid":2457282,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"歐盟制裁4中國官員及一機構 包括前黨委副書記朱海侖 中方即晚反制","createTime":"2021-03-22T13:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T17:36:49.000Z","uid":239336,"like":77,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"3ffdbb79963e9932a005c6ba277fa94d04eeffa0","tid":2457282,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"【新增中國回應】歐盟周一宣佈，就中國侵犯新疆維吾爾人的人權作出制裁，分別有4名中國官員與1個實體被實施旅遊禁令與凍結資產。中國即晚實施反制措施，制裁10名人員和4個實體。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟對4名中國官員與1個實體實施旅遊禁令與凍結資產等制裁，被制裁人士分別為前政法委書記朱海侖，新疆維吾爾自治區黨委常委王明山，新疆生產建設兵團政委、中國新建集團公司董事長王君正，及新疆維吾爾自治區公安廳廳長陳明國，至於被制裁的實體則為新疆生產建設兵團公安局。<br />\n德新社周一較早時間引述歐盟消息人士指出，歐盟外長會議已達成協議，歐盟會就中國侵犯新疆維吾爾人的人權制裁中國，會議上同時通過對緬甸及俄羅斯等涉及侵犯人權的人士實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部周一堅決反對和強烈譴責歐盟制裁，指歐盟惡意傳播謊言和虛假信息，干涉中國內政，宣佈制裁10名人員和4個實體。<br />\n被制裁人員包括：歐洲議會對華關系代表團團長包瑞翰（Reinhard B&uuml;tikofer）、歐洲議會議員蓋勒（Michael Gahler）、歐洲議會人權小組副主席 （Rapha&euml;l Glucksmann）格魯克斯曼、庫楚克（Ilhan Kyuchyuk）、曾倡為港人設「救生艇」的萊克斯曼（Miriam Lexmann），荷蘭議會議員舍爾茨瑪（Sjoerd Wiemer Sjoerdsma），比利時議會議員科格拉蒂（Samuel Cogolati），立陶宛議會議員薩卡利埃內（Dovile Sakaliene），研究新疆集中營的德國學者鄭國恩（Adrian Zenz），瑞典學者葉必揚（Bjorn Jerden）。<br />\n<br />\n至於被制裁的機車為歐盟理事會政治與安全委員會，歐洲議會人權分委會，德國墨卡託中國研究中心，丹麥民主聯盟基金會。相關人員及其家屬被禁止入境中國內地及香港、澳門特別行政區，他們及其關聯企業、機構也已被限制同中國進行往來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210322/ESFYJOENAJBM5PRUWDYH42MXXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210322%2FESFYJOENAJBM5PRUWDYH42MXXE%2F&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=4f4c68b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210322%2FESFYJOENAJBM5PRUWDYH42MXXE%2F&h=6e59ab7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210322/ESFYJOENAJBM5PRUWDYH42MXXE/</a>"},{"pid":"f5432c6aed7ae75ace0cb0b57d781666fdf04e69","tid":2457282,"uid":239336,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uh9VB2H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuh9VB2H.gif&h=7f2b1ce8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87c7145b15899672d4da23855f39ce97c63784c9","tid":2457282,"uid":51271,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"支那仲諗住o係歐洲議會過歐支貿易協議?"},{"pid":"d3482c77eae044376fb0fa13d293dea68c94c8a6","tid":2457282,"uid":2054,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"87c7145b15899672d4da23855f39ce97c63784c9","tid":2457282,"uid":51271,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"支那仲諗住o係歐洲議會過歐支貿易協議?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:40:45.000Z","msg":"屎加速師唔會令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e01c01d44d169e144ce07a8d4a2b92b00f43ad","tid":2457282,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d3482c77eae044376fb0fa13d293dea68c94c8a6","tid":2457282,"uid":2054,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"87c7145b15899672d4da23855f39ce97c63784c9","tid":2457282,"uid":51271,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"支那仲諗住o係歐洲議會過歐支貿易協議?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:40:45.000Z","msg":"屎加速師唔會令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">台灣又唔計</span>"},{"pid":"9d1e1e33675a4f37313deb3b70e2ff7321098736","tid":2457282,"uid":321002,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"咦，勁喎，反制裁10個加4家實體，14：5大勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7cfda33ea4c053ca31bd949f2d9a6d2264dd43","tid":2457282,"uid":2054,"like":7,"